	   Teemu Ikonen <tpikonen@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~), bzip2, dkms, libpopt-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.6
Homepage: http://www.peak-system.com/fileadmin/media/linux/index.htm
